2. Project Overview
Purpose

The AI-Driven Emotion Detection & Personalized Learning Support Platform is designed to understand students' emotions from text and provide personalized learning assistance. The platform analyzes learner input using deep learning models and generates supportive, emotion-aware responses using Generative AI.

Instead of manually interpreting student concerns, the system automatically detects emotional states such as confusion, frustration, curiosity, boredom, and confidence, enabling educators and learners to receive instant guidance.

3. Objectives
Detect student emotions from free-text input.
Provide personalized learning guidance using AI.
Improve student engagement through emotion-aware responses.
Reduce response time for academic support.
Track emotional trends for future analysis.
Support self-paced learning with intelligent recommendations.
4. Features
User-friendly Streamlit interface
Emotion Detection using BiLSTM
Emotion Detection using BERT
Mixed Emotion Prediction
AI-generated Personalized Learning Support
Gemini AI Integration
Confidence Score Visualization
Emotion Analytics Dashboard
CSV Interaction Logging
Model Comparison (BiLSTM vs BERT)
Rule-based Keyword Enhancement
Real-time Response Generation
